{"tid":1669230,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【納米樓玩L完】龍床盤菁雋驚現8宗連環撻大定 殺定118萬元","createTime":"2019-10-22T12:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T13:29:29.000Z","uid":66271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eed8af8bac8863e7621bbe4191ddbe51eea71e04","tid":1669230,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191022/large/1571736239_1812.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191022%2Flarge%2F1571736239_1812.jpg&h=10ba1fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府上周三公佈施政報告後，全城二手急起動，不過，挾面積「細絕全城」又稱為「龍床盤」的屯門菁雋，發展商3個月前開賣，卻一連氣錄得8宗撻大定，涉及金額2,356萬元<br />\n<br />\n內房佳源國際（2768）、舖王鄧成波家族持有的菁雋，按一手住宅銷售網顯示，項目連環出現8宗撻大定個案，單位全部低於200方呎「納米戶」，由實用面積164至171方呎，而且全是7月14日簽定臨時買賣合約，同月簽定正式買賣合約。<br />\n<br />\n上述8宗撻定個案交易，全部於10月21日公佈終於買賣合約，一律採用60天付款，成交價介乎272萬至325萬元，若以交易金額10%作定金計算，料殺定117.8萬元。因發展商一句「皇宮那麼大，皇帝都只是睡一張龍床」一鳴天下響的「龍床盤」菁雋，最細面積僅128方呎開放式戶，惹起全城關注，今年7月份開售時，首批最平285萬元，雖然單位面積狹小，仍一度熱賣。<br />\n<br />\n菁雋於今年7月14日劈價重推，惟其後有消息指，有多個主要銀行因「爆quota」而叫停批出菁雋的即供按揭，令部份買家失去預算，不少買家望發展商延長成交期讓他們有足夠時間上會。市場估計，有關撻定不排除是買家購入後未能承造按揭而選擇撻定。"},{"pid":"46ced9b8660cc7a58ab0147450771e3b1d3a180a","tid":1669230,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzwN9Bw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzwN9Bw.png&h=7b697f90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"924aed95a26f59a1807763edb9855be136f34a2f","tid":1669230,"uid":105490,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:41:34.000Z","msg":"不自量力姐 大家放心 大市解讀"},{"pid":"7a78cfb468811ce50483a71b3e737579a2092c99","tid":1669230,"uid":270563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0246361d78388b065efd6e95db455542a1c75b3a","tid":1669230,"uid":133828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"棟野主要係地點西姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試下係中環，大把撚樣炒上幾球<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58f4dc0189f8e29579825dfd27fba1445c04f22","tid":1669230,"uid":153427,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:58:49.000Z","msg":"在電訊盈科中心旁邊才值這價錢"},{"pid":"bddb6b84cf14fdd5a08733190743a8878cda8b35","tid":1669230,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"向西潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2697018d2a0b142637456d3202b5d2c2119aae3b","tid":1669230,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"諗起麥明詩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c349fa89d345b429d63b50f8a488b343f0452d8a","tid":1669230,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"係時候低吸"},{"pid":"66179ab55ccde7323ad134d043c69e72ed78cdfe","tid":1669230,"uid":28068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:13:08.000Z","msg":"多謝林鄭啦<br />\n無佢班買家都唔敢撻訂"},{"pid":"c11533e5d0b02ae9b6b3053e336ca6405ab19300","tid":1669230,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"加價重推 上400萬先 反正有得借"},{"pid":"8e901ac513616d55040be6a231ec5fdc91f853b3","tid":1669230,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"市場估計，有關撻定不排除是買家購入後未能承造按揭而選擇撻定。"}]}